OL,6,FChildren will be taught how to spot
OL,7,Fextremist content and fake news online
OL,8,Funder plans announced by the
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,12,Fsaid she was launching a review of the
OL,13,Fcurriculum in primary and secondary
OL,14,Fschools to embed critical thinking
OL,15,Facross multiple subjects and arm
OL,16,Fchildren against "putrid conspiracy
OL,17,Ftheories."
